2) Evaluation of the two candidates against that preference:
- America - The Complete Greatest Hits (Classic Rock; Album-Oriented Rock/AOR): As a greatest-hits compilation from a well-known classic-rock act, this CD is likely to contain many familiar, concise songs with strong melodic hooks and polished production. AOR typically emphasizes cohesive album-quality production and radio-friendly arrangements, which suit listening on CD (consistent mastering, predictable track lengths, and a smooth listening flow). For a general CD enthusiast who values a satisfying listening experience without requiring a specific niche taste, a greatest-hits collection maximizes immediate enjoyment and replayability.
