In short: Candidate 1 better fulfills my core desires for close, intimate vocal presentation, analogue‑ish warmth and dynamic, album‑oriented storytelling; Candidate 2, while well mastered and melodic, leans into short, singles‑style listening and the greatest‑hits framing that I try to avoid.

